<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.8">
<l>immaikku mēḻēḻ piṟavikkum paṟṟāvāṉ</l>
<l>nammai yuṭaiyavaṉ nārā yaṇaṉnampi</l>
<l>cemmai yuṭaiya tirukkai yāṟṟāḷpaṟṟi</l>
<l>ammi mitikkak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that the perfect Nārāyaṇa—He who is [our] Support</l>
<l>in this life and seven times seven births, our Owner—</l>
<l>held [my] foot with [His] red sacred hand</l>
<l>and had [me] tread upon the grinding-stone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
